'''接合菌门'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|Zygomycota}}）是一类[[真菌|真菌]]。 其孢子分為有性及無性兩種，有性生殖為接合孢子，無性生殖為孢囊孢子；此門菌物的菌絲屬於「無隔多核」。

== 分類 ==

傳統上依據形態將真菌分為'''接合菌門'''（Zygomycetes）、[[子囊菌門|子囊菌門]](Ascomycetes)、及[[担子菌門|担子菌門]](Basidiomycetes)，然而許多傳統上因為形態簡單被視為接合菌的真菌因為分子證據而被移入子囊菌（如[[青黴菌|青黴菌]]、[[黑黴菌|黑黴菌]]）；分子證據也顯示接合菌是一個[[姐妹群|姐妹群]]。

2007年，[[戴维·希贝特|戴维·希贝特]]（David Hibbett）将接合菌门分为4个[[亚门|亚门]]：[[毛霉亚门|毛霉亚门]]、[[梳霉亚门|梳霉亚门]]、[[虫霉亚门|虫霉亚门]]和[[捕虫霉亚门|捕虫霉亚门]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Hibbett |first1=David S. |last2=Binder |first2=Manfred |last3=Bischoff |first3=Joseph F. |last4=Blackwell |first4=Meredith |last5=Cannon |first5=Paul F. |last6=Eriksson |first6=Ove E. |last7=Huhndorf |first7=Sabine |last8=James |first8=Timothy |last9=Kirk |first9=Paul M. |last10=Lücking |first10=Robert |last11=Thorsten Lumbsch |first11=H. |last12=Lutzoni |first12=François |last13=Matheny |first13=P. Brandon |last14=McLaughlin |first14=David J. |last15=Powell |first15=Martha J. |last16=Redhead |first16=Scott |last17=Schoch |first17=Conrad L. |last18=Spatafora |first18=Joseph W. |last19=Stalpers |first19=Joost A. |last20=Vilgalys |first20=Rytas |last21=Aime |first21=M. Catherine |last22=Aptroot |first22=André |last23=Bauer |first23=Robert |last24=Begerow |first24=Dominik |last25=Benny |first25=Gerald L. |last26=Castlebury |first26=Lisa A. |last27=Crous |first27=Pedro W. |last28=Dai |first28=Yu-Cheng |last29=Gams |first29=Walter |last30=Geiser |first30=David M. |last31=Griffith |first31=Gareth W. |last32=Gueidan |first32=Cécile |last33=Hawksworth |first33=David L. |last34=Hestmark |first34=Geir |last35=Hosaka |first35=Kentaro |last36=Humber |first36=Richard A. |last37=Hyde |first37=Kevin D. |last38=Ironside |first38=Joseph E. |last39=Kõljalg |first39=Urmas |last40=Kurtzman |first40=Cletus P. |last41=Larsson |first41=Karl-Henrik |last42=Lichtwardt |first42=Robert |last43=Longcore |first43=Joyce |last44=Miądlikowska |first44=Jolanta |last45=Miller |first45=Andrew |last46=Moncalvo |first46=Jean-Marc |last47=Mozley-Standridge |first47=Sharon |last48=Oberwinkler |first48=Franz |last49=Parmasto |first49=Erast |last50=Reeb |first50=Valérie |last51=Rogers |first51=Jack D. |last52=Roux |first52=Claude |last53=Ryvarden |first53=Leif |last54=Sampaio |first54=José Paulo |last55=Schüßler |first55=Arthur |last56=Sugiyama |first56=Junta |last57=Thorn |first57=R. Greg |last58=Tibell |first58=Leif |last59=Untereiner |first59=Wendy A. |last60=Walker |first60=Christopher |last61=Wang |first61=Zheng |last62=Weir |first62=Alex |last63=Weiss |first63=Michael |last64=White |first64=Merlin M. |last65=Winka |first65=Katarina |last66=Yao |first66=Yi-Jian |last67=Zhang |first67=Ning |title=A higher-level phylogenetic classification of the Fungi |journal=Mycological Research |date=2007-05-01 |volume=111 |issue=5 |pages=509–547 |doi=10.1016/j.mycres.2007.03.004}}</ref>，2011年[[坷·霍夫曼|坷·霍夫曼]]（Käthe Hoffmann）又增加了一个[[孢霉亚门|孢霉亚门]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Hoffmann |first1=K. |last2=Voigt |first2=K. |last3=Kirk |first3=P.M. |title=Mortierellomycotina subphyl. nov., based on multi-gene genealogies |journal=Mycotaxon |date=2011-05-09 |volume=115 |issue=1 |pages=353–363 |doi=10.5248/115.353}}</ref>。2014年虫霉亚门升为[[虫霉门|虫霉门]]<ref>{{cite book |title=Systematics and evolution : part a. |publisher=Springer |location=[Place of publication not identified] |isbn=978-3-662-49578-0}}</ref>。2016年，Joseph W. Spatafora根据[[基因组|基因组]]数据将接合菌门重新拆分为[[捕虫霉门|捕虫霉门]]和[[毛霉门|毛霉门]]，其中捕虫霉门包括[[虫霉亚门|虫霉亚门]]、[[梳霉亚门|梳霉亚门]]和[[捕虫霉亚门|捕虫霉亚门]]，毛霉门包括[[球囊霉亚门|球囊霉亚门]]、[[被孢霉亚门|被孢霉亚门]]和[[毛霉亚门|毛霉亚门]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Spatafora |first1=Joseph W. |last2=Chang |first2=Ying |last3=Benny |first3=Gerald L. |last4=Lazarus |first4=Katy |last5=Smith |first5=Matthew E. |last6=Berbee |first6=Mary L. |last7=Bonito |first7=Gregory |last8=Corradi |first8=Nicolas |last9=Grigoriev |first9=Igor |last10=Gryganskyi |first10=Andrii |last11=James |first11=Timothy Y. |last12=O’Donnell |first12=Kerry |last13=Roberson |first13=Robert W. |last14=Taylor |first14=Thomas N. |last15=Uehling |first15=Jessie |last16=Vilgalys |first16=Rytas |last17=White |first17=Merlin M. |last18=Stajich |first18=Jason E. |title=A phylum-level phylogenetic classification of zygomycete fungi based on genome-scale data |journal=Mycologia |date=2016-09 |volume=108 |issue=5 |pages=1028–1046 |doi=10.3852/16-042}}</ref>。

{{fact|因為過去的研究較少，加上[[系統發生學|系統發生學]]不斷引入各種新的分子技術和統計學模型，真菌的分類目前時常發生大幅變動，目前較新的分類方式是將接合菌分成下列四支}}：

*[[黴菌綱|黴菌綱]] Mucoromycotina
**[[Endogonales|Endogonales]]
**[[毛黴目|毛黴目]] Mucorales
**[[Mortierellales|Mortierellales]]
*[[Kickxellomycotina|Kickxellomycotina]]:
**[[Asellariales|Asellariales]]
**[[Kickxellales|Kickxellales]]
**[[Dimargaritales|Dimargaritales]]
**[[Harpellales|Harpellales]]
*[[Entomophthorales|Entomophthorales]]
*[[Zoopagales|Zoopagales]]

